94	      <div>
95	        <h1>DreamTeam Eval Dashboard</h1>
96	        <p>Browse eval runs, track agent performance, and drill into traces.</p>
97	      </div>
98	      <a href="/evals/new" class="btn-new-run">+ New Run</a>
